quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,169,"My Lord, save me and my family from [the consequence of] what they do."
  26,170,"So We saved him and his family, all,"
  26,171,"Except an old woman{1} among those who remained behind.",footnotes:1:Lot's wife, who had collaborated with the evildoers.
  33,22,"And when the believers saw the companies, they said, "
  33,23,"Among the believers are men true to what they promised Allāh. Among them is he who has fulfilled his vow [to the death], and among them is he who awaits [his chance]. And they did not alter [the terms of their commitment] by any alteration -"
  33,24,"That Allāh may reward the truthful for their truth and punish the hypocrites if He wills or accept their repentance. Indeed, Allāh is ever Forgiving and Merciful."
  34,1,"[All] praise is [due] to Allāh, to whom belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is in the earth, and to Him belongs [all] praise in the Hereafter. And He is the Wise, the Aware."
  34,2,"He knows what penetrates into the earth and what emerges from it and what descends from the heaven and what ascends therein. And He is the Merciful, the Forgiving."
  34,3,"But those who disbelieve say, ",footnotes:1:Or "the weight of a small ant."